    "img": "https://westendtherapy.ca/ws/media-library/5254cef2b1244a5fc2b5e6226a7edcd4/waiting-room-v2.jpeg",
    "excerpt": "West End Therapy is excited to announce the renovation and expansion of our Winnipeg clinic, creating a more welcoming and comfortable space for our clients.",
    "body": "<p>We are thrilled to share some exciting news with our clients and community: West End Therapy has completed a significant renovation and expansion of our clinic space at 759 Wall Street in Winnipeg.</p>\n\n<h2>A Space Designed for Healing</h2>\n<p>We have always believed that the physical environment matters for therapy. A calm, welcoming, and private space helps clients feel at ease and supports the important work that happens in sessions. Our renovation was designed with exactly this in mind — creating a space that communicates safety, warmth, and professionalism from the moment you walk in.</p>\n<p>The expanded clinic now includes additional therapy rooms, allowing us to serve more clients and accommodate the growing demand for our services in the West End community and across Winnipeg. We have also updated our waiting area and common spaces to be more comfortable and welcoming.</p>\n\n<h2>Growing to Meet Community Need</h2>\n<p>The renovation reflects something we are deeply grateful for: the trust our community has placed in us since we opened in 2020. The demand for quality mental health services in Winnipeg continues to grow, and we are committed to expanding our capacity to meet that need.</p>\n<p>Over the past few years, we have grown our team significantly, adding therapists with diverse specializations to ensure that clients can find the right fit for their needs. The expanded physical space allows us to continue this growth.</p>\n\n<h2>Our Commitment</h2>\n<p>Whether you are a long-standing client or are considering reaching out for the first time, we want you to know that our commitment to providing compassionate, evidence-based therapy in a safe and welcoming environment remains at the heart of everything we do.</p>\n<p>We look forward to welcoming you to our refreshed space. If you haven't already, we'd love to hear from you — fill out our intake form or give us a call at (204) 809-9114.</p>"
